lead_paragraph: Kyle Lowry scored a career-high 43 points to help the Toronto Raptors beat the Eastern Conference-leading Cleveland Cavaliers 99-97 Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Lowry Scores Career-High 43 as Raptors Beat Cavaliers, 99-97
